tafsir[50]{c,v,t}:
  77,1,"Alla woondirii keneeli dewandirﾉ擁 hono siiru puccu."
  77,2,"O woondiri keneeli bippooji bippugol."
  77,3,"O woondiri keneeli carooji toﾉ登 cargol."
  77,4,"O wooniri malayke en tellinooji ko seernata hakkunde goongo e meere."
  77,5,"O woondiri malayka en tellinooji wahyu."
  77,6,"Hoﾉ擁 tellina wahyu okkoowo ngantu ummaade ka Alla faade e aade en e jeertinde ﾉ兎 lepte Alla."
  77,7,"Ko podante ﾉ熔n ko e ummital e haasbeede e njoﾉ電i ko ko arata sikke alah heen."
  77,8,"Si annoore koode e ndaaygu mum momtaama."
  77,9,"Si kammu on fettii sabi tellaade Malayka en e mammba."
  77,10,"Si pelle ﾉ蓉ggitaama e nokku mum en ﾉ容 kelta haa ngonti sollaaru."
  77,11,"Saanga nde Nelaaﾉ兎 ndennina e waktu dottaaﾉ熔."
  77,12,"ﾃｱalawma mawﾉ熔 dirtinaama ngam seedaade e leﾆｴﾆｴi mum en."
  77,13,"E ﾃｱalngu ceerndugol hakkunde jiyaaﾉ兎, feeﾃｱa hakkunde mbo goonga e mbo meere, e malaaﾉ熔 e kiitaaﾉ熔."
  77,14,"Hol ko anndin Ma-aan nelaaﾉ熔-ko woni ﾃｱalngu ceerndugol."
  77,15,"Halkaare e lepte e perte e oon ﾃｱalawma woodanii fennuﾉ兎 ko nelaaﾉ兎 ngaddi ummaade ka Alla."
  77,16,"Mbela Min kalkaana leﾆｴﾆｴi gadinooﾉ擁 nde njedduno penni Nulaaﾉ兎 mum en?."
  77,17,"Refti Min bndewna heen cakkatiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎, Min kalkaﾉ兎 no Min kalkiri mon nih."
  77,18,"Ko hono no Min kalkiri ﾉ擁in leﾆｴﾆｴi, Min kalkirta fennuﾉ兎 ko Nelaaﾉ熔 addi ko."
  77,19,"Halkaare e lepte woodanii wonande ﾉ兎en fennooﾉ兎 njbdi mum en ﾃｱande ﾃｱalngu njoﾉ電i."
  77,20,"Mbela Min tagaani mon- onon aade en-ummaade e ndiyam kouﾉ預m ko ﾉ預am woni toﾉ橡兎re maniyyu."
  77,21,"Min mbaﾉ擁 ndiyam ﾉ預m e nokku deenaaﾉ熔 ko oon woni rannga debba."
  77,22,"Haa e dumunna ganndaaﾉ熔 ko oon woni yonto caawgol suko."
  77,23,"Min koddiri sifa jibinaaﾉ熔 o mbaadi makko e ko nanndi heen, heskey Oon koddirﾉ熔 ﾉ蓉um fof Minen."
  77,24,"Halkaare e lepte e perte woodanii wonande ﾉ兎en fennooﾉ兎 baawal Alla."
  77,25,"Mbela Min mbaﾉ預ani leydi ndi na sooma aade en fof."
  77,26,"Hondi renndini wonﾉ兎 heen wuurﾉ兎 e maayﾉ兎 ubbaaﾉ兎 e hendi ."
  77,27,"Min mbaﾉ擁 e hendi pelle tabitﾉ容, na ndeena ndi e dillude toowﾉ容, Min njarndi mon ndiyam mbelﾉ預m, tagﾉ熔 ﾉ蓉um horataaka umminde mon."
  77,28,"Halkaare e lepte woodanii wonande ﾉ兎en fennooﾉ兎 njoﾉ電i mum en ﾃｱande ﾃｱalngu jnobdi."
  77,29,"Wiyanee fennooﾉ兎 ko nelaaﾉ兎 ngaddi ko- onon fennoobe- kuuﾆｴe faade ko pennatnaﾉ熔n ko e lepte."
  77,30,"Njahee faade e mbeelu cuurki yiit mbanndi cate tate."
  77,31,"ﾆ「uﾉ登l ﾉ熔wdi alah toon, ndi haﾉ預tah lew lewndu yiite e nguli mum yande e mon."
  77,32,"Yiite nge na werlo peete, kala heen wootere Alla no mawniri a sikkat ko huﾉ兎ere."
  77,33,"Peete werleteeﾉ容 Alla noﾉ容 ﾉ殿lwiri e noﾉ容 mawniri a sikkat koﾉ容 geloobi ﾉ殿leeji."
  77,34,"Halkaare woodanii wonande ﾉ兎en fennooﾉ兎 njoﾉ電i mum en ﾃｱande ﾃｱalngu jnobdi."
  77,35,"E o ﾃｱalngu ﾉ兎 kaalatah hay huunde."
  77,36,"ﾆ‘ cakkitantaake sabu ﾉ兎 ngantina faade e joom mum en ko faati e keefeeru e bone mum en, ﾉ兎 ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬ra Mbo ngantu."
  77,37,"Halkaare e perte woodanii ﾉ兎en fennooﾉ兎 kabaruuji ﾃｱalngu jnobdi."
  77,38,"O ko ﾃｱalngu ceerndugol hakkunde tagaaﾉ容, Min ndenndinii on e leﾆｴﾆｴi gadiiﾉ擁 e dingiral gootal."
  77,39,"Si tawii hoﾉ熔n ndaﾃｱi feere nde puuntiraton haa ndaﾉ熔n e lepte Alla pewjanee lan."
  77,40,"Halkaare woodanii wonande ﾉ兎en fennooﾉ兎 njoﾉ電i mum en ﾃｱande ﾃｱalngu jnoﾉ電i."
  77,41,"Pellet ﾉ兎en reentiriiﾉ兎 joom mum siinude jamirooje Alla e reentaade kaﾉ容 Makko, hoﾉ兎 e nder ﾉ熔wdi lekﾉ容 aljanna e ceewle ndiyam belﾉ容 ilooje."
  77,42,"E ﾉ兎snaaﾉ容 ﾉ容ﾉ兎 tuuyate ﾃｱaamde."
  77,43,"ﾆ‘ wi*anee:ﾃｱaame e laaﾉ橡擁, njaron njaram mbelﾉ預m ﾉ預m alah lorla, sabu ko golle mon moﾆｴﾆｴe ka aduna."
  77,44,"Yeru ndi njoﾉ電i ndi Min njoﾉ妬 mon, ko hono ndi Min njoﾉ妬rta labinﾉ兎 golle mum en."
  77,45,"Halkaare e lepte e perte woodanii ﾉ兎en fennooﾉ兎 ko Alla heblani hulﾉ兎 e jnoﾉ電i."
  77,46,"Fennuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 na wiyee:ﾃｱaame ndakmitaﾉ熔n e wela wela nguurndam tuma setta ka aduna, ko on bonﾉ兎 sabu ko pennuﾉ熔n ko Alla e nelaaﾉ兎 Makko."
  77,47,"Halkaare woodanii wonande ﾉ兎en fennooﾉ兎 njoﾉ電i mum en ﾃｱande ﾃｱalngu jnoﾉ電i."
  77,48,"Si ﾉ兎e fennooﾉ兎 mbiyaama: njuule ngam Alla ﾉ兎 njuulatah."
  77,49,"Halkaare e lepte e perte e oon ﾃｱalawma woodanii fennuﾉ兎 ko nelaaﾉ兎 ngaddi ko ummaade ka Alla."
  77,50,"Siﾉ兎 goonﾉ擁naani oo Quraana tellinaaﾉ熔 ummaade ka Alla honde yeewtere woﾉ溶de ﾉ兎 goonﾉ擁nta?."
